---
/**
 * The "må pugges" flag: a formula that isn't on the exam sheet and so must be
 * memorised. Shared by <Formula> (inline panels) and <FormulaSheet> (rows) so the
 * treatment lives in ONE place. A soft amber tint in the house borderless
 * tinted-surface recipe (the Flexoki aside treatment). Positioning is the parent's job — a `flex: 1` sibling
 * (the label/description) pushes this to the row's trailing edge.
 */
---

<span class="memorize-badge sc-kicker" title="Står ikke på formelarket – må pugges">
  må pugges
</span>

<style>
  /* Mono uppercase kicker recipe comes from .sc-kicker; the badge adds its
     amber tinted-surface fill, size and padding. */
  .memorize-badge {
    flex: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--warning);
    background: var(--warning-bg);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xs);
    padding: 0.2em 0.6em;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
</style>
